OL,3,CThree companies face prosecution over
OL,4,CHinkley Point C death
OL,6,FThree companies are facing prosecution
OL,7,Fover health and safety offences
OL,8,Ffollowing the death of a worker at the
OL,9,FHinkley Point C nuclear construction
OL,10,Fsite in Somerset.
OL,12,FJason Waring, 48, from
OL,13,FNottinghamshire, died in a
OL,14,Fconstruction incident in November 2022.
OL,16,FMr Warning worked for one of the
OL,17,Fsite's contractors Bylor, a joint
OL,18,Fventure between two of the companies
OL,19,Falso facing charges - Bouygues Travaux
OL,20,FPublics SAS and Laing O'Rourke
OL,21,FDelivery Limited.
