OL,3,CThree companies face prosecution over
OL,4,CHinkley Point C death
OL,6,FThe third company involved is NNB
OL,7,FGeneration Company (HPC) Ltd, which is
OL,8,Fa subsidary created by EDF Energy to
OL,9,Fbuild Hinkley.
OL,11,FThe decision to bring legal
OL,12,Fproceedings follows an investigation
OL,13,Fby the Office for Nuclear Regulation
OL,14,F(ONR) - the UK's independent nuclear
OL,15,Fregulator.
OL,17,FThe investigation examined the
OL,18,Fcircumstances surrounding Mr Waring's
OL,19,Fdeath and the health and safety
OL,20,Fpractices at the site.
