OL,3,CThree companies face prosecution over
OL,4,CHinkley Point C death
OL,6,FDetails about the specific charges
OL,7,Fbeing brought against the three
OL,8,Fcompanies, as well as the location and
OL,9,Fdate of the first court hearing, will
OL,10,Fbe announced once these have been
OL,11,Ffinalised.
OL,13,FThe office has previously emphasised
OL,14,Fthat nuclear projects must operate
OL,15,Funder the strictest health and safety
OL,16,Fprotocols given the nature of the work
OL,17,Finvolved.
