OL,3,CThree companies face prosecution over
OL,4,CHinkley Point C death
OL,6,FHinkley Point C is one of the UK's
OL,7,Fmost significant nuclear construction
OL,8,Fprojects, representing a major
OL,9,Finvestment in the country's future
OL,10,Fenergy infrastructure.
OL,12,FThe site has been under construction
OL,13,Ffor several years and involves complex
OL,14,Fcivil engineering works being carried
OL,15,Fout.
OL,17,FThe ONR has stated it is unable to
OL,18,Fprovide further comment at this time,
OL,19,Fdue to active legal proceedings.
